<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Nina haja nawe
 Kila saa;
 Hawezi mwingine
 Kunifaa.

[V2]
 Yesu, nakuhitaji
 Vivyo kila saa!
 Niwezeshe, Mwokozi,
 Nakujia.

[V3]
 Nina haja nawe;
 Kaa nami,
 Na maonjo haya,
 Hayaumi.

[V4]
 Nina haja nawe;
 Kila hali,
 Maisha ni bure,
 Uli mbali.

[V5]
 Nina haja nawe,
 Nifundishe
 Na ahadi zako
 Zifikishe.

[V6]
 Nina haja nawe,
 Mweza yote,
 Ni wako kabisa
 Siku zote.</lyrics>
<title>Nina haja nawe TZR11</title>
<hymn_number>11</hymn_number>
</song>